videos.description: Iowa's Joe Wieskamp slips on the floor and Lamar Stevens grabs the ball and takes it the other way for the jam.

videos.description: Off the turnover, Penn State's Lamar Stevens rocks the rim to bring the crowd at the Palestra to its feet.
